1. create a script
2. make it executable
3. accept two parameters , a name and fav sport
4. Display any sentence to the screen using the inp


answer

#! /bin/bash

NAME=$1
FAV_SPORT=$2
echo "Hello $1 , your fav sport is $2"



running

chmod 755 sports.sh
./sports.sh Abhi football


output 



[abhi@fedora bash_scripts]$ ./sports.sh Abhi circkter
Hello Abhi , your fav sport is circkter
